To be honest, the art needs improvement. Shading, lineart, etc. And theee anatomy is a bit off as well. Still, overall good. As for the storyline, I think it's a bit sudden and rushed. In my opinion, it'd be nice if the characters go nice and slow, not just showing the dick right away, cuz when you build it up more, you thrill the audience more. For the dialogues, they're okay but some kinda takes time to process or understand, maybe it's in the grammar or usage of words, syempre, kasi English. They're fine, but they're kinda off too. But in general, this is really a good start! Especially for a beginner artist. My advice is to practice more, and get more into the story so every page is worth reading. Looking forward to a longer and better one next time. Way to go!
